data.description: Well maintained brick home in one of the most desirable Ammon neighborhoods. Ideal location to Hillview Elementary and just steps away from McCowen Park.  On the main floor you'll find original hardwood flooring and a gas fireplace, perfect for those cold winter nights.  The kitchen and dining area have new tile flooring, complemented by well-preserved original cabinetry. Two bedrooms on the main floor share a full bath with newly updated tile floors and tub/shower surround. The fully finished basement affords a spacious family room perfect for family game nights or watching the game.  A second gas fireplace, and two additional bedrooms with a full bathroom. Enjoy the oversized 2-car garage, a backyard shed, and a generous .27-acre fenced yard for kiddos to play or pets to roam. In you new home you'll be close to shopping and entertainment with out all the busy traffic.
